Symbol.Script_FWM:
actualGUID = FROM_GUID
! ============================================================================== ! Subroutines ! ==============================================================================
_startID = "6CE99B5C-CF43-49DE-BAE1-A97F3F28D683" _endID = "A2A8D348-1ABA-45B9-A8CE-23673C76F715" gosub "New_ScreenSizeHandling_FWM"
! ============================================================================== ! Set migration GUID ! ==============================================================================
setmigrationguid actualGUID
! ============================================================================== end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! en ! ==============================================================================
! ============================================================================== ! New screen size handling: adding and deleting parameters ! ============================================================================== "New_ScreenSizeHandling_FWM": if actualGuid = _startID then
bHas = STORED_PAR_VALUE("iMonitorType", _iMonitorType) |\ DELETED_PAR_VALUE("iScreenRatio", _iScreenRatio) |\ DELETED_PAR_VALUE("bUnitSizing", _bUnitSizing)
if _iMonitorType = 1 then if _iScreenRatio = 4 then ! Custom Screen Ratio actualGuid = "" else if _bUnitSizing = 0 then iScreenRatio = 4 screenWidth = A - 0.03 ! Frame thickness * 2 screenHeight = ZZYZX - ZZYZX / 7 - 0.03 ! Frame thickness * 2, Supporter Height
parameters iScreenRatio = iScreenRatio, screenHeight = screenHeight, screenWidth = screenWidth else iScreenSize = 8 ! Custom Screen Diagonal Size parameters iScreenSize = iScreenSize endif actualGuid = _endID endif else actualGuid = _endID endif endif return
Symbol.Script_BWM:
targetGUID = TO_GUID
! ============================================================================== ! Subroutines ! ==============================================================================
gosub "New_ScreenSizeHandling_BWM"
! ============================================================================== ! Set migration GUID ! ==============================================================================
setmigrationguid targetGuid
! ============================================================================== end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! en ! ==============================================================================
! ============================================================================== ! Deleting Screen Size parameters, extending the Laptop Type values ! ============================================================================== "New_ScreenSizeHandling_BWM": if targetGUID # "" then newparameter "bUnitSizing", "Boolean" newparameter "st_screenSize", "String" newparameter "screenRatioRate", "RealNum"
if iScreenRatio = 4 then ! Cut migration in case of Custom Screen Ratio targetGUID = "" else bUnitSizing = 1 parameters bUnitSizing = bUnitSizing
if iMonitorType = 2 & iScreenSize = 8 then targetGUID = "" ! Cut migration in case of Custom Screen Size endif endif endif return
